@RMA.Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5299

### Đăng nhập với Local Test Account
# @name login
POST {{RMA.Server_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Test API bảo mật (Firebase / Local JWT)
GET {{RMA.Server_HostAddress}}/api/auth/test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
